There are two types of authorisations:

**ONE**

- Methods of killing not specified in schedule 1

*Specify method: xxxxxxx* (free text)

- Setting free and re-homing of protected animals after completion of a series or regulated procedures

*Provide details of the circumstances under which this may occur (see section 17A of the Act, subsection 3 and 4)* (free text)

------------------------------

**Additional conditions** should be free text (add another etc - Does not need title, they just become a numbered list)
